VChris Anderson: Thank you. I have,
p408
aVand I'm sure everyone here has,
p409
aVA) a hundred questions, B) wants to hug you.
p410
aVI'm just going to ask you one quick question.
p411
aVWhen you first start this and you bring in a flock of animals,
p412
aVit's desert. What do they eat? How does that part work?
p413
aVHow do you start?
