aa(lp415
VAllan Savory: Well, we have done this for a long time,
p416
aVand the only time we have ever had to provide any feed
p417
aVis during mine reclamation,
p418
aVwhere it's 100 percent bare.
p419
aVBut many years ago, we took the worst land in Zimbabwe,
p420
aVwhere I offered a £5 note
p421
aVin a hundred-mile drive
p422
aVif somebody could find one grass
p423
aVin a hundred-mile drive,
p424
aVand on that, we trebled the stocking rate,
p425
aVthe number of animals, in the first year with no feeding,
p426
aVjust by the movement, mimicking nature,
p427
aVand using a sigmoid curve, that principle.
p428
aVIt's a little bit technical to explain here, but just that.
